b'So I\xe2\x80\x99m not sure who threw that name out but it was brought up and we discussed it for less than 5 min, no shit, we decided to call ourselves Jimmy Eat World so we could play this dumb ass party. My memory was that it was a Valentines Day Party but not sure.'

b'Tom and Rick (who wasn\xe2\x80\x99t in the band quite yet) played in a band together that would change their name for every show. Me, zach, would go to a lot of those shows and I was there when they called themselves \xe2\x80\x9cJimmy Eat World\xe2\x80\x9d and it stuck with me.'

b'So we took a break from the garage and huddled around our kitchen island and decided to play the show but at that time, we hadn\xe2\x80\x99t yet sorted out a name so we needed to figure that out ASAP.'
